{"tid":765993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Zombie Boy 殭屍男孩 Rick Genest 自殺享年 32 歲！","createTime":"2018-08-03T08:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T15:53:51.000Z","uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"30ccb1278efc6bd208b712c95790c1eb7f3a4d3b","tid":765993,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T08:41:32.000Z","msg":"大家記得那帥氣十足，滿身骷髏刺青的男模 Zombie Boy 殭屍男孩嗎？目前證實過世，享年 32 歲，於週三被發現在加拿大蒙特利爾的公寓內自殺。殭屍男孩本名為 Rick Genest，他在 16 歲的時候得到自己的第一個刺青，在 19 歲的時候就全身都滿滿的刺青了。原本將在 8 月 7 日過 33 歲生日的 Rick Genest，但現在選擇結束自己的生命。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.gq.com.tw/_rs/645/userfiles/sm/sm1024_images_A1/36880/2018080336525329.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.gq.com.tw%2F_rs%2F645%2Fuserfiles%2Fsm%2Fsm1024_images_A1%2F36880%2F2018080336525329.jpg&h=51f56c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nZombie Boy 殭屍男孩 Rick Genest 最早被 Lady Gaga 的造型師發現，然後於 2011 年在 Lady Gaga《Born This Way》MV 中出鏡，也從這裡開始成名，名聲也是傳遍時尚圈。之後更出演了電影《浪人47 47 Ronin》以及影集《Silent Witness》。那帥氣的刺青樣貌在世界各地擁有不少粉絲，在 15 歲被告知有腦瘤的他，手術完成活了下來，這回則過不去心病，與世長辭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.gq.com.tw/_rs/645/userfiles/sm/sm1024_images_A1/36880/2018080336537213.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.gq.com.tw%2F_rs%2F645%2Fuserfiles%2Fsm%2Fsm1024_images_A1%2F36880%2F2018080336537213.png&h=a82eda80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而從出鏡了 Lady Gaga《Born This Way》MV 便與 Lady Gaga 相識，這回 Lady Gaga 也在 Twitter 表示「我們要改變這樣的文化環境，並且重視心理的健康。如果你很痛苦，請打給你的家人朋友尋求幫助，我們必須要拯救彼此。」<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.gq.com.tw/entertainment/culture/content-36880.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gq.com.tw%2Fentertainment%2Fculture%2Fcontent-36880.html&d=ubKrzgiQmVzJPhp33jvs0mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6d86acb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gq.com.tw/entertainment/culture/content-36880.html</a>"},{"pid":"8ee54cde8480bd917fb085f68b0b87c530f73a25","tid":765993,"uid":17103,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"塊面咁撚樣, 日日起身見住 .. 真係死撚左好過"},{"pid":"225541f0ae06656d6ddcfadb201d92af03b8296f","tid":765993,"uid":939,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ee54cde8480bd917fb085f68b0b87c530f73a25","tid":765993,"uid":17103,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"塊面咁撚樣, 日日起身見住 .. 真係死撚左好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔去死?"},{"pid":"013224a8900e8628fc2cc2c0434a7dd5847c04a5","tid":765993,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ee54cde8480bd917fb085f68b0b87c530f73a25","tid":765993,"uid":17103,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"塊面咁撚樣, 日日起身見住 .. 真係死撚左好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"賓周問題"},{"pid":"9e28449f3b4f7fc03591cb539745b21613c88417","tid":765993,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"225541f0ae06656d6ddcfadb201d92af03b8296f","tid":765993,"uid":939,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ee54cde8480bd917fb085f68b0b87c530f73a25","tid":765993,"uid":17103,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"塊面咁撚樣, 日日起身見住 .. 真係死撚左好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"咁點解你唔去死?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"因為我唔係佢咁撚樣囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef434816fe194fd92610a99c44f36b7bbf7921bb","tid":765993,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"記得新聞講<br />\n佢紋全身係博彈起 <br />\n<br />\n估唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}